data.name: One Hundred Coin
data.description:
The project claims to have developed a atable proof-of-stake with 100 coins as fixed reward per block and variable block times of 1 to 10 minutes. It is claimed that ONE coin was designed as a low cost, lower power, low-income friendly solution to mining bitcoins.
